01:00:06,360 --> 01:00:07,760
 umjesto da ste doma

1601
01:00:07,760 --> 01:00:09,300
 i da gledate utakmicu

1602
01:00:09,300 --> 01:00:10,700
 i pijete pivu,

1603
01:00:10,760 --> 01:00:13,960
 i to što sam rekao,

1604
01:00:13,960 --> 01:00:14,220
 onak,

1605
01:00:14,220 --> 01:00:14,880
 molitva,

1606
01:00:14,880 --> 01:00:16,580
 molitva,

1607
01:00:16,580 --> 01:00:18,880
 mi moramo biti oslonac

1608
01:00:18,880 --> 01:00:19,860
 i mi svi,

1609
01:00:19,860 --> 01:00:21,020
 i velim,

1610
01:00:21,020 --> 01:00:23,120
 molitva zajednička

1611
01:00:23,120 --> 01:00:23,640
 je nešto,

1612
01:00:23,640 --> 01:00:24,860
 nama je jako onak,

1613
01:00:24,860 --> 01:00:25,920
 jako važna

1614
01:00:25,920 --> 01:00:27,020
 i jako velika stvar

1615
01:00:27,020 --> 01:00:28,660
 i naravno,

1616
01:00:28,660 --> 01:00:29,920
 prvo moramo znati sami

1617
01:00:29,920 --> 01:00:31,420
 molit,

1618
01:00:31,420 --> 01:00:32,940
 da bi kasnije mogli znati

1619
01:00:32,940 --> 01:00:35,020
 i voditi nekoga drugog u molitvi

1620
01:00:35,020 --> 01:00:36,960
 i naći neki način

1621
01:00:36,960 --> 01:00:39,040
 koji međusobno nam funkcionira.

1622
01:00:39,040 --> 01:00:39,920
 Onak,

1623
01:00:40,760 --> 01:00:42,320
 prepustimo se gospodinu,

1624
01:00:42,320 --> 01:00:43,700
 to sam bore

1625
01:00:43,700 --> 01:00:46,100
 napisao isto,

1626
01:00:46,100 --> 01:00:48,040
 često se brinemo

1627
01:00:48,040 --> 01:00:49,700
 kakav će biti naš budući partner,

1628
01:00:49,700 --> 01:00:50,380
 pa sad ono,

1629
01:00:50,380 --> 01:00:51,360
 razmišljamo,

1630
01:00:51,360 --> 01:00:52,440
 mora biti takav i takav.

1631
01:00:52,440 --> 01:00:54,440
 Isus zna kakav ti treba.

1632
01:00:54,440 --> 01:00:56,380
 Ak neko zna,

1633
01:00:56,380 --> 01:00:57,480
 zna Isus.

1634
01:00:57,480 --> 01:00:58,480
 Tako da ono,

1635
01:00:58,480 --> 01:00:59,860
 ajmo se prepustiti,

1636
01:00:59,860 --> 01:01:01,140
 ajmo vjerovati,

1637
01:01:01,140 --> 01:01:02,620
 ajmo onako živjeti

1638
01:01:02,620 --> 01:01:03,620
 prave brakove

1639
01:01:03,620 --> 01:01:05,160
 kakve trebamo živjeti

1640
01:01:05,160 --> 01:01:05,920
 i na kakve nas

1641
01:01:05,920 --> 01:01:06,980
 gospodin poziva.

1642
01:01:06,980 --> 01:01:08,400
 Amen.

1643
01:01:10,760 --> 01:01:12,900
 Hvala što pratite kanal.

